copy.title: rolipoliPainting
copy.instruction0: Use the paddle to bounce the roly-poly bug. He'll spread the dye as he rolls over your material.
copy.instruction1: The roly-poly bug will bounce off the pin-bumpers.
copy.instruction2: Color as much of the material as you can before your dye runs out.
copy.title: Roly-Poly Painting

copy.bobbinEncourage2: Keep him rolling, keep him rolling!
copy.bobbinEncourage4: You're doing a stitch-arific job so far!
copy.bobbinEncourage5: Do ya think roly-polies get dizzy?
